General.Name: Turbo Mech Bhd
General.Description: Turbo-Mech Berhad, an investment holding company, sells rotating equipment and spare parts for the oil and gas, petrochemical, and chemical industries primarily in Malaysia, Singapore, Indonesia, the Philippines, Thailand, Vietnam, Brunei, and internationally. It offers pumps, compressors, and turbines. The company also provides maintenance and overhaul services. In addition, it provides pump performance test and packaging skids mounted equipment for oil and gas and other related industry. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.
